  "description": "Commvault Crypto Library (CVCL) is a cryptographic software module used in various products by Commvault Systems, Inc. The module provides a collection of Approved and Non-Approved cryptographic services for key generation, symmetric and asymmetric encryption, hash, HMAC and signature generation/verification.",
